SUMMARY:TK-3rd Grade Alignment
LOCATION:Santa Clara County Office of Education\, Ridder Park Drive\, San Jose\, CA\, USA
DESCRIPTION:ONLY FOR TK-3rd: The session will focus on the California Preschool through Third Grade (PK-3) Learning Progressions which map the developmental pathways of children's knowledge and skills over time. They ensure continuous\, developmentally appropriate education by linking early learning foundations to later elementary standards across five core developmental domains.\n\nThe session will be recorded\; therefore\, a waiver must be signed upon arrival and check-in.\n\nThere will be assigned seating.
END:VEVENT
